Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case takes place\Nin a department store at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The empty floors after closing time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even under the cover of night,\Nthere is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Department Store Hijack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have you now, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him to hell, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Yaiba, shall defend world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in high school. So what\Nam I doing watching this drivel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like Yaiba, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it! Go, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for shopping with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We look forward\Nto seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba! Yaiba! He fights\Nfor justice! Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba's autograph is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to treasure it\Nfor my entire life, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we took the picture\Nwith Yaiba, I seem to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the picture, Ayumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to recall Genta saying\Nthat he was hungry when we took this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I bought a hot dog and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at that shop! I'm going to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the place is closed by now.\NI say leave it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!\NI'm going to go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. My deductive skills\Nare to blame for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry! The security system\Nis going to activate in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun. That door's going to lock\Nwhen the security system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get it in less than 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! My treasure's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to Conan-kun's\Ngreat detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better hurry before\Nthe security system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the security guards' office\Ninside the building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and explain the situation,\NI'm sure they'll let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security Office! Floor B2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Yaib--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jewelry store's\Non the 6th floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And there are antiques in\Nthe convention hall on the 7th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the elevator lady--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. We have until morning\Nto take whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gang of thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble if they find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill us! Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the elevator lady\Nand those other people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's stay hidden\Nand contact the police! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! There's no dial tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cord's been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phones must be down\Nbecause of the security system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So nobody's going to come to rescue us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat a ton of eel lunches\Nbefore I get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robbers will hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up! The windows here\Nare made of especially thick glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! There's a weird sound\Ncoming from the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Use the security cameras\Nto check out the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan! What about the window?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! You won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange?! Those were\Nsome pretty loud sounds we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's take the loot and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Let's check it out just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, aren't there\Nany exits around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, you little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko and I got caught up\Nin a discussion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've seen our faces! Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! Do you read me?!\NTurn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? I didn't copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bunch of\Nlittle brats in the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd those lousy kids go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other guys in the security office\Nknow we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned on the lights to catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun still hasn't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know\Nwhere that lousy kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Get out! Everyone out! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They almost had us trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save that for after\Nwe get out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Conan was\Nat the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he go with his friends\Nto see some kids' show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch dark outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try calling the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my food, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to starve me to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Marutan Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We need to get as far away\Nfrom them as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be open during our\Nregular hours tomorrow, from 10 am--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? So what do you say you\Nmake me some dinner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Kojima household?\NThis is Mori Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Genta-kun--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have this department store surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your weapons down\Nand release the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no police here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They used a\Nbunch of stupid mannequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Yoshida residence?\NI'm Conan Edogawa's--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ayumi-chan hasn't\Ncome home yet either?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a call from\NMitsuhiko-kun's family too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, Genta! Do you\Nwant them to catch you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized something strange,\Nbut I don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan and his friends were kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the only explanation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Did any of their families\Nreceive ransom demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that they're taking\Ntheir sweet time coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's about some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Cook me some food already--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the investigation department?\NInspector Megure, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Works better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real liability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any incidents at the moment\Nthat might involve the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is strange that none of them\Nhave returned home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could something have happened to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put out a bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they'll turn up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll excuse me, I'm in\Nthe middle of an important case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've done all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All there is to do now is wait\Nfor any reports about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted\Nto do this at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us. We'll pay for\Nthis if we make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we even will\Nmake it out alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so down, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had plenty to eat now,\Nso cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take care of them\Nand get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the\NJunior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Junior Detective League...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it must be a pretty important case\Nif they're still at it this late....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that Conan-kun\Nand the others aren't important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn that Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm missing my dinner thanks to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gang of department store thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sneak in after the stores close\Nand steal jewelry and electronics...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the important\Ncase he was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Department store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Commence counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where are they hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't handle alcohol well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay! We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for the Junior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for the Junior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, we're in danger--\Nthere are some bad people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say,\Nthe 5th member of the thief gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a 5th person who\Nactivated the escalator earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person had been waiting\Nto catch all four of us at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the remaining people\Nin the security office,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were the only one who knew\Nhow many of us there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned in advance to get inside\Nby getting a job as an elevator girl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you could scout out the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deductive work, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems you didn't know that\NI was actually the gang's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pistol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll lure her onto the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's over, little boy!\NCome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basketballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your pointless resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the thieves!\NTake them into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of silly kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:27.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:41.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:57.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:05.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:11.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:21.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:26.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The following day, we were\Ngiven an award ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for capturing the thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for any of the things we ate\Nor broke inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chalk another one up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the Junior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we were taping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.19,0:24:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder might be recorded on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was the one who\Nsmeared her dress with blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The June Bride Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.23,0:24:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is pretty difficult, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
